'''''Coz Ov Moni 2 ( FOKN) -'''''lni film y'umuziki wa [[Gana]] yasohotse 2013 yakozwe na FOKN BOIS kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wamafirime wigenga wo muri [[Gana]] King Luu. Filime numuziki uvugwa byose ni  mucyongereza cya Pidgin , ariko subtitles zirerekanwa.<ref>https://foknbois.bandcamp.com/album/coz-ov-moni-2-fokn-revenge-o-s</ref><ref>https://fantasticfest.com/films/coz-ov-moni-2</ref> ni filime yamenyekanye cyane muri Gana kuko ikurura abakunzi bumuziki ndetse na filimi<ref>https://nwfilm.org/films/coz-ov-moni-2-fokn-revenge/</ref>.<ref>https://www.rockol.com/uk/album-19275959/Fokn-Bois-Coz-Ov-Moni-2-(Fokn-Revenge)-O.S</ref> 

== Kurekura ==
